author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Basic Partner performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 03, 2024. 

Songs:
NEW DECADE (00:00)
WASTING TIME (03:44)
THEM (09:32)

Anton Brachet - Drums
Clément Le Gallo - Lead Singer, Keyboard , Saxophone
Sacha Sourty - Guitar, Keyboard
Marius Vicet - Bass, Vocals
Audio & Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Audio Mixer: Christophe Hogommat

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Scott Holpainen
